The dataset used in this project is available for download via the link provided below.
Due to its large size (over **8 GB** for training and testing data), it is hosted externally rather than included directly in the repository:

> **Dataset Download Link:**
> https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tLjykxrj-n2MJvNjlQEXsAXWTxsOSuVx/view?usp=drive_link

Please download the dataset and place it under the `Code/dataset` directory, keeping the same folder structure as specified in the usage instructions.
